  m_text: 'Jester''s Labyrinth of Laughter - a horror maze game.

    Your goal in
    this game is to find the exit door while keeping a distance from the clowns.
    You can hold flashlight on the clowns to kill them.

    Controls: WASD to Move,
    Hold Right Click for Flashlight, E for Sonar Wave, F on exit door for escaping.

    Song
    Credits -  The fine art of poisoning by jill tracy

    Made by Vado <3

'
